  "dct_description_sm": [
    "Japan City Migration Census Data, 2015 is a polygon theme representing Cities (市/区/町/村) in Japan as of 2015. This map is georeferenced to the surface of the earth and fit to World Geodetic System (1984) coordinates. Attribute data include summary results of the 2015 Japanese census questions regarding migration. The documentation of these variables can be found in the \"CITY_Migration\" sheet tab from the accompanying code book. This dataset is part of Japan 2015 Census collection."
  ],
